---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-inner">
		<p class="footer-tagline">
			<strong>re-money-lab</strong>｜元買取業界8年の本音メディア
		</p>
		<p class="footer-desc">
			元買取営業8年・累計査定3万点超の筆者ハルが、不用品を後悔せず売る方法を業界の裏側から本音で解説しています。
		</p>
		<div class="footer-links">
			<a href="/">ホーム</a>
			<a href="/blog">記事一覧</a>
			<a href="/about">運営者情報</a>
		</div>
		<div class="social-links">
			<a href="https://www.threads.net/@re_money_lab" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
				<span class="sr-only">Threads</span>
				<svg viewBox="0 0 192 192" aria-hidden="true" width="22" height="22">
					<path
						fill="currentColor"
						d="M141.537 88.988a66.667 66.667 0 0 0-2.518-1.143c-1.482-27.307-16.403-42.94-41.457-43.1h-.34c-14.986 0-27.449 6.396-35.12 18.036l13.779 9.452c5.73-8.695 14.724-10.548 21.348-10.548h.229c8.249.053 14.474 2.452 18.503 7.129 2.932 3.404 4.892 8.11 5.864 14.05-7.314-1.243-15.224-1.626-23.68-1.14-23.82 1.371-39.134 15.264-38.105 34.568.522 9.792 5.4 18.216 13.735 23.719 7.047 4.652 16.124 6.93 25.557 6.413 12.458-.683 22.231-5.436 29.057-14.127 5.184-6.602 8.46-15.156 9.9-25.94 5.91 3.564 10.292 8.257 12.711 13.9 4.115 9.591 4.355 25.35-8.5 38.193-11.265 11.254-24.808 16.122-45.275 16.272-22.708-.167-39.883-7.453-51.045-21.65-10.45-13.292-15.851-32.5-16.054-57.096.203-24.596 5.604-43.804 16.054-57.097 11.162-14.197 28.337-21.482 51.045-21.65 22.87.168 40.343 7.489 51.948 21.776 5.69 7.001 9.983 15.815 12.821 26.041l16.345-4.346c-3.448-12.591-8.875-23.471-16.284-32.59C140.298 9.883 118.305.197 90.31 0h-.114C62.259.197 40.51 9.92 25.567 28.91 12.272 45.8 5.41 69.310 5.196 95.808l-.001.094.001.092c.214 26.5 7.076 50.01 20.371 66.898 14.943 18.99 36.692 28.713 64.629 28.91h.114c24.836-.172 42.36-6.677 56.795-21.106 18.886-18.866 18.317-42.534 12.087-57.063-4.469-10.41-12.997-18.871-24.654-24.645z"
